PAWNATHON CANADA is an exciting four-day event taking place April 1-4 in Toronto. Attendees will be offered a free appraisal on their prized items, and the opportunity to potentially sell their treasures to a Pawn Master. Expert appraisers will be on site to look at every item, and participants may be filmed to appear in PAWNATHON CANADA, a new special airing on History Television in summer 2011. The most extraordinary items - based on history, mystery and value - will be included in a bidding war where Pawn Masters will go head-to-head in a battle to outbid each other for the most coveted items. Please visit www.pawnathon.com to pre-register for the event
